The '''Kyrotech Corporate Combine''' was a company which produced the [[Kyrotech Blademaster X-260]] series of [[Assassin droid/Legends|assassin droids]]. They programmed all of their [[Droid/Legends|droids]] with a sub-routine which would not allow them to act against the interests of the Combine.<ref name="Polyhedron68">{{PolyhedronCite|68|Iron Hands, Captive Hearts}}</ref>

